column2: SELECT    p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,     (p.u-p.r) as &&&, (p.r-p.i) as &&&, (p.r-p.z) as &&&, (p.g-p.r) as &&&,    p.type as obj_ph_type,    s.specobjid, s.class, s.subclass, s.z as redshift into mydb.DR1#_spec_samp from PhotoObj AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE    s.z BETWEEN # AND #   AND (p.u-p.r <= #)   AND (p.r-p.i <= #)   AND (p.r-p.z <= #)   AND (p.g-p.r >= (p.r-p.i) + #)   AND (p.u-p.r >= #*(p.r-p.z))
